BEGIN_TEXT
Compute the following limit using L'Hospital's rule if appropriate.
Use INF to denote \(\infty\) and MINF to denote \(-\infty\).
$PAR
\( \displaystyle \lim_{x\to\infty} \left(1-\frac{$aa}{x}\right)^x\) =  \{ ans_rule()\}
END_TEXT

